29:08.841 --> 29:10.957
What are you doing, Gus?

29:15.721 --> 29:18.076
Well, I was buildin' a doggy door.

29:18.761 --> 29:21.195
What's goin' on around here, Gus?

29:23.401 --> 29:25.392
Why did you dig up my wife?

29:27.641 --> 29:29.757
Cos I wanted to fuck her.

29:36.561 --> 29:38.517
I hate it when that happens.

29:44.201 --> 29:44.997
No.

29:45.121 --> 29:47.077
Got a permit for this?

29:51.281 --> 29:53.158
I didn't think so.

29:57.481 --> 29:59.437
Let me know if this hurts.

30:09.521 --> 30:12.672
No brain, no pain. Think about it.

30:32.481 --> 30:35.041
Remember, Chase, I had Renee first.

31:56.401 --> 31:58.153
Marjorie.

31:58.801 --> 32:00.757
Jeff?

32:06.401 --> 32:09.154
Did you really think
you could be like me?

32:40.961 --> 32:42.030
Mom.

32:43.561 --> 32:45.836
I came back for you, Jeff.

32:46.121 --> 32:48.476
We're going to be together again.

33:40.601 --> 33:42.876
We can try again, Chase.

33:47.001 --> 33:48.673
Oh, my God.

33:50.241 --> 33:52.516
We can make it work this time.

33:55.921 --> 33:57.479
No.

34:04.801 --> 34:07.269
Don't you love me any more, Chase?

34:07.401 --> 34:09.437
You're not Renee.

34:10.721 --> 34:12.677
Renee's dead.

34:16.440 --> 34:18.476
Get away from her, Jeff.

34:22.241 --> 34:24.197
Get away.

34:25.960 --> 34:28.918
Jeff, honey,
why don't you go downstairs?

34:31.440 --> 34:33.591
Your father and I need to talk.

34:43.481 --> 34:45.039
Jeff.

34:47.281 --> 34:49.237
I love you.

34:50.641 --> 34:52.597
I love you more.

35:01.321 --> 35:03.152
- Hey, junior.
- Shit.

35:03.281 --> 35:05.431
Wanna play?

35:17.161 --> 35:19.117
Looks like Daddy got a boo-boo.

35:23.201 --> 35:25.351
Now, where were we?

36:16.841 --> 36:20.595
Here it comes, buddy.
Here it fucking comes.

36:32.201 --> 36:35.432
You're gonna die, junior.

36:40.801 --> 36:42.712
Eat this, asshole.

37:08.041 --> 37:10.157
- Come on, Dad.
- Get out.

37:13.081 --> 37:15.037
I'm gonna get you outta here, Dad.

37:15.161 --> 37:16.913
Come here.

37:32.641 --> 37:34.597
I'm melting.

37:41.081 --> 37:44.517
Jeff, honey, what are you doing?

37:46.001 --> 37:46.956
No.

37:48.761 --> 37:50.797
You're not gonna leave me, Jeff.

37:54.041 --> 37:58.319
Your father and I are
trying to work things out.

38:01.281 --> 38:05.638
Jeff, I don't wanna be alone.

38:09.521 --> 38:11.955
Come back, Jeff.

38:14.321 --> 38:15.879
I love you.

38:16.681 --> 38:20.356
She's not your mom, Jeff. Let's go.

38:22.761 --> 38:24.717
Stay with me.

38:25.481 --> 38:27.119
Dead is better.

38:34.041 --> 38:36.635
Stay with me.

39:12.161 --> 39:14.117
You all set?

39:14.841 --> 39:16.797
Let's go.

39:42.721 --> 39:45.155
I never had anyone die before.

39:46.121 --> 39:48.316
But I guess you get over it.

39:48.441 --> 39:50.397
I mean, eventually.

39:51.881 --> 39:53.917
You never get over it.

